What kind of picture?

31
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:36,430
A picture of that rumored girl.

32
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:39,340
And stuff from middle school, like when we became
the badminton club's representatives.

33
00:01:39,370 --> 00:01:43,080
- I'm confiscating this.
- Give it back! What's there to be shy about?

34
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:46,415
You're always so embarrassed.
You'll never grow if you don't embrace it.

35
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,520
