Look.

48
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:26,630
Before, whenever I was getting along with my friends,

49
00:03:27,130 --> 00:03:28,130
you'd always...

50
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:30,370
I'm over that now.

51
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:33,240
I know you like me.

52
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,240
Besides,

53
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:42,590
I'm confident no one's going to steal you away.

54
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:46,470
I see.

55
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,430
It's good that you're not bothered by it.

56
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:52,170
However,

57
00:03:54,638 --> 00:03:56,400
