- Hey, badminton club members...

75
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,510
So sweet.

76
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:55,370
Here, open wide...

77
00:04:56,230 --> 00:04:57,800
- Is it good?
- He says it's pretty good.

78
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,860
