might've wanted to be alone.

92
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,730
Be alone?

93
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:57,750
Oh.

94
00:05:58,130 --> 00:05:59,330
You mean me and Watarai?

95
00:05:59,610 --> 00:06:00,610
Yeah.

96
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:02,330
I mean, look.

97
00:06:03,990 --> 00:06:06,530
I've been trying not to ask, but...

98
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,480
um...

99
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:13,870
Yeah.

100
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,830
You two are dating, right?

101
00:06:17,550 --> 00:06:18,550
Huh?

102
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,000
