185
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,150
but then,

186
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:26,100
they'd probably confiscate it at school.

187
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,750
So I figured,

188
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,260
something you could wear at school,

189
00:10:29,450 --> 00:10:30,450
during club activities,

190
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,950
anytime, anywhere,

191
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,140
would be better.

192
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:38,800
Also,

193
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,460
to be honest,

194
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,430
if you wore it every day,

195
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:45,030
it would make me really happy.

196
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:54,340
Oh.

197
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,480
Just now,

198
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:57,300
