202
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:35,700
I'll leave it at this for today.

203
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,550
I'll just have to be patient.

204
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:44,770
Well,

205
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:46,090
