206
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,280
Don't tell me...

207
00:11:55,810 --> 00:11:57,650
I overwhelmed you again?

208
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:05,040
I don't think I'll ever

209
00:12:05,190 --> 00:12:06,700
be a match for him.

210
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:08,790
Come on.

211
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:10,130
- Let's go.
- Okay.

212
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:12,100
Yeah.

213
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,420
Whether we end up together

214
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:21,020
or not...

215
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:23,360
Just being with him...

216
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:26,590
makes me feel like I could be this happy forever.

217
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,220
But...

218
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:30,700
Someday...

