244
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:23,750
Hioki.

245
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,390
Here.

246
00:14:25,950 --> 00:14:26,950
I just need you here, Hioki.

247
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,040
I...

248
00:14:29,110 --> 00:14:30,420
