274
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:48,840
Yeah.

275
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:51,190
We could go to the beach

276
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,620
or the mountains.

277
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,140
We could go to so many places.

278
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:00,560
During spring break,

279
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:03,220
I want to see you

280
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:04,930
