00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:47,180
What did you...

291
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:49,270
just say?

292
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:52,490
I want you to go out with me.

293
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:58,150
In other words...

294
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:01,920
I want you to be my boyfriend.

295
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:19,540
Watarai?

296
00:17:21,370 --> 00:17:22,370
It's nothing.

297
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:26,470
I just feel so pathetic.

298
00:17:26,930 --> 00:17:27,930
Huh?

299
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:31,120
Because...

300
00:17:32,890 --> 00:17:34,970
I was supposed to be the one to say that.

301
00:17:37,470 --> 00:17:38,570
What are you talking about?

302
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:42,320
Let me be the cool one for a change.

303
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:48,470
But...

304
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,320
you're already cool.

305
00:17:54,290 --> 00:17:55,290
Because...

306
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:58,210
confessing takes so much courage,

307
00:17:58,890 --> 00:18:01,060
yet you always manage to put your feelings into words

308
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:02,810
and tell me everything.

309
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,750
I think...

310
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,280
that's really amazing.

311
00:18:09,660 --> 00:18:10,760
You are too.

312
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:15,820
Oh.

313
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:18,130
So,

314
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:20,360
uh...

315
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:24,500
Are you really

316
00:18:25,490 --> 00:18:26,690
sure you want me?

317
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:30,250
Yeah.

318
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:33,150
I want you.

319
00:18:33,170 --> 00:18:34,570
It has to be you.

320
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,500
I like you so much.

321
00:18:50,450 --> 00:18:52,150
I'll be in your care from now on.

322
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,450
As your boyfriend.

323
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:02,520
Oh, boyfriend...

324
00:19:02,950 --> 00:19:04,380
Ah, wait...

325
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:06,120
I'll... I'll be in your care too.

326
00:19:07,610 --> 00:19:08,680
Why are you getting shy?

327
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,820
I am not!

328
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:12,470
So cute.

329
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:23,080
Look at me.

330
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:17,940
Well then,

331
00:20:18,490 --> 00:20:19,590
shall we go?

332
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:21,780
Yeah.

333
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,680
- Come on, let's go.
- Okay.

334
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:52,080
(Class 2-5, Thank You!)

335
00:20:55,950 --> 00:20:58,040
In the grand scheme of life,

336
00:20:59,570 --> 00:21:01,410
high school

337
00:21:02,210 --> 00:21:04,040
is just a small part of it.

338
00:21:07,620 --> 00:21:08,620
But,

339
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:13,090
meeting new friends

340
00:21:14,610 --> 00:21:15,710
and falling in love...

341
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,250
Oh, you're finally here!

342
00:21:19,360 --> 00:21:20,660
What took you so long?

343
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:23,160
Weren't we all supposed to go get
conveyor belt sushi?

344
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:24,340
Oh, sorry, sorry.

345
00:21:30,250 --> 00:21:31,250
I can't believe this.

346
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,480
Hm?

347
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:35,550
Right now,

348
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,650
I think I'm getting a little carried away with happiness.

349
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:40,370
Me too.

350
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:45,150
Hey, have those two
forgotten about us?

351
00:21:45,190 --> 00:21:46,190
Totally.

352
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:47,890
They're always like this.

353
00:21:48,190 --> 00:21:49,190
Hey!

354
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:50,430
You two over there.

355
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,780
You're obviously getting carried away.

356
00:21:51,860 --> 00:21:52,860
Oh, sorry, sorry.

357
00:21:53,230 --> 00:21:55,090
I really only had eyes for Watarai just now.

358
00:21:55,390 --> 00:21:56,390
Huh?

359
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:57,770
Hey, you too?

360
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:59,040
You two are so lovey-dovey.

361
00:21:59,150 --> 00:22:00,150
Let's go.

362
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,040
Let's go.

363
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,500
Sharing a laugh with everyone...

364
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:34,360
those days we spent together...

365
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:38,980
I'm sure,

366
00:22:39,990 --> 00:22:40,990
that in the future,

367
00:22:41,140 --> 00:22:42,410
no matter how old we get,

368
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:45,760
these memories will last a lifetime

369
00:22:46,780 --> 00:22:49,280
and stay in our hearts forever.
